Individual.comment:
Rajanaka Kashmiri Pandit We are known as 'Raina' - that is our family name. Raina appears to be a corruption of 'Rajanaka', for that is really the original name of our family. We were also known as 'Razdan'. This appears to be a Persianised form of the same name 'Rajanaka'.
(Extract from the Diary of ShivJi raina)
